description: A kinder-guardian can ask How To Destiny where to find certain materials, how to get the the lighthouse, and how to increase their light level. It has a humor element to it with more skills being added over time.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, Ask How To Destiny where do I find spinmetal?
How do I increase my light level?
name: How To Destiny
shortDescription: How To Destiny is a spoof app that helps kinder-guardians find their way around Destiny.
